<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201014/e8fa4948fa2d4cf380e976092b54ae92.jpeg" img_width="405" img_height="270" /></p>
<p>雅安市石棉县黄果柑丰收。</p>
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201014/a472581f31694c4e9dcac6f2a8bed0d8.jpeg" img_width="410" img_height="231" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
